snippet.title: 12 Rounds Against Satan Movie Trailer
snippet.description:
From the books sequels of 12 Rounds Against Satan 1st Edition and 12 Rounds Against Satan 2nd Edition for Teens. Meet the first half of 12 Rags Team (12 Rounds Against Satan Series). 

These six individuals who worship together has taken a oath of Renewing their Spirit in Baptism and sworn to fight against Satan and his Demon Trick Monsters who have terrorized the city.  

Their identity has been kept private and now they are forced to team up to fight against Satan's Legion of Demon Tricks. Stay tuned and see what happenings next!
